  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide shelter for 100  HIV/AIDS positive women</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There are many widows in Uganda living with HIV /AIDS especially in rural areas with a huge burden of orphans, no food security, poor shelter, and no scholastic material resulting into high drop out rates especially in girls. With support of this project there will be reduced school drop out, improved shelter, reduced malnutrition in households, reduced stigma among people with HIV/AIDS  and reduction in further spread of the pandemic.</narrative>
  </description>
